{
  "video_id": "rCplocVemjo",
  "title": "Tim Berners-Lee: A Magna Carta for the web",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12895.0,
      "end_time": 14543.0,
      "text": "TED is 30."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14543.0,
      "end_time": 17180.0,
      "text": "The world wide web is celebrating this month"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17181.0,
      "end_time": 19453.0,
      "text": "its 25th anniversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19453.0,
      "end_time": 22142.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve got a question for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22142.0,
      "end_time": 26966.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about the journey, mainly about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26966.0,
      "end_time": 28681.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about the state."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28681.0,
      "end_time": 30995.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about what sort of a web we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30995.0,
      "end_time": 34315.0,
      "text": "So 25 years ago, then, I was working at CERN."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34315.0,
      "end_time": 36665.0,
      "text": "I got permission in the end after about a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36665.0,
      "end_time": 39297.0,
      "text": "to basically do it as a side project."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39297.0,
      "end_time": 40995.0,
      "text": "I wrote the code."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40995.0,
      "end_time": 43144.0,
      "text": "I was I suppose the first user."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43144.0,
      "end_time": 45687.0,
      "text": "There was a lot of concern"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45687.0,
      "end_time": 47205.0,
      "text": "that people didn&#39;t want to pick it up"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47206.0,
      "end_time": 49300.0,
      "text": "because it would be too complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49300.0,
      "end_time": 50749.0,
      "text": "A lot of persuasion, a lot of wonderful"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50749.0,
      "end_time": 52459.0,
      "text": "collaboration with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52459.0,
      "end_time": 54888.0,
      "text": "and bit by bit, it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54888.0,
      "end_time": 56531.0,
      "text": "It took off. It was pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56531.0,
      "end_time": 59748.0,
      "text": "And in fact, a few years later in 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59748.0,
      "end_time": 63949.0,
      "text": "five percent of the world population"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63950.0,
      "end_time": 65769.0,
      "text": "were using the world wide web."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65769.0,
      "end_time": 68480.0,
      "text": "In 2007, seven years later, 17 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68480.0,
      "end_time": 71820.0,
      "text": "In 2008, we formed the World Wide Web Foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71820.0,
      "end_time": 73393.0,
      "text": "partly to look at that"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73394.0,
      "end_time": 76244.0,
      "text": "and worry about that figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76244.0,
      "end_time": 78303.0,
      "text": "And now here we are in 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78303.0,
      "end_time": 80536.0,
      "text": "and 40 percent of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80537.0,
      "end_time": 84553.0,
      "text": "are using the world wide web, and counting."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84553.0,
      "end_time": 86554.0,
      "text": "Obviously it&#39;s increasing."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86555.0,
      "end_time": 89963.0,
      "text": "I want you to think about both sides of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89963.0,
      "end_time": 92179.0,
      "text": "Okay, obviously to anybody here at TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92180.0,
      "end_time": 95163.0,
      "text": "the first question you ask is, what can we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95163.0,
      "end_time": 97219.0,
      "text": "to get the other 60 percent on board"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97219.0,
      "end_time": 98538.0,
      "text": "as quickly as possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98539.0,
      "end_time": 100854.0,
      "text": "Lots of important things. Obviously it&#39;s going to be around mobile."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100854.0,
      "end_time": 102834.0,
      "text": "But also, I want you to think about the 40 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102834.0,
      "end_time": 104544.0,
      "text": "because if you&#39;re sitting there yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104544.0,
      "end_time": 107170.0,
      "text": "sort of with a web-enabled life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107170.0,
      "end_time": 108466.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t remember things anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108466.0,
      "end_time": 110179.0,
      "text": "you just look them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110180.0,
      "end_time": 114263.0,
      "text": "then you may feel that it&#39;s been a success"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114263.0,
      "end_time": 116243.0,
      "text": "and we can all sit back."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116243.0,
      "end_time": 119326.0,
      "text": "But in fact, yeah, it&#39;s been a success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119326.0,
      "end_time": 121271.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s lots of things, Khan Academy"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121272.0,
      "end_time": 123561.0,
      "text": "for crying out loud, there&#39;s Wikipedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123561.0,
      "end_time": 125378.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a huge number of free e-books"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125378.0,
      "end_time": 126784.0,
      "text": "that you can read online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 126784.0,
      "end_time": 128551.0,
      "text": "lots of wonderful things for education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128550.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130274.99999999999,
      "text": "things in many areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 130276.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132678.0,
      "text": "Online commerce has in some cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132678.0,
      "end_time": 135469.0,
      "text": "completely turned upside down the way commerce works altogether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 135469.0,
      "end_time": 137240.0,
      "text": "made types of commerce available"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137240.0,
      "end_time": 139350.0,
      "text": "which weren&#39;t available at all before."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 139350.0,
      "end_time": 142732.0,
      "text": "Commerce has been almost universally affected."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 142732.0,
      "end_time": 144999.0,
      "text": "Government, not universally affected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144999.0,
      "end_time": 147112.0,
      "text": "but very affected, and on a good day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 147112.0,
      "end_time": 150790.0,
      "text": "lots of open data, lots of e-government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 150800.0,
      "end_time": 152783.0,
      "text": "so lots of things which are visible"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 152783.0,
      "end_time": 154410.0,
      "text": "happening on the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 154411.0,
      "end_time": 156522.0,
      "text": "Also, lots of things which are less visible."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 156522.0,
      "end_time": 158924.0,
      "text": "The healthcare, late at night when they&#39;re worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158925.0,
      "end_time": 160636.0,
      "text": "about what sort of cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160636.0,
      "end_time": 162761.0,
      "text": "somebody they care about might have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162761.0,
      "end_time": 167767.0,
      "text": "when they just talk across the Internet to somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167767.0,
      "end_time": 172276.0,
      "text": "who they care about very much in another country."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172276.0,
      "end_time": 176495.0,
      "text": "Those sorts of things are not, they&#39;re not out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176495.0,
      "end_time": 179715.0,
      "text": "and in fact they&#39;ve acquired a certain amount of privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179715.0,
      "end_time": 182499.0,
      "text": "So we cannot assume that part of the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182499.0,
      "end_time": 183590.0,
      "text": "part of the deal with the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183590.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "is when I use the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188416.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just a transparent, neutral medium."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188416.0,
      "end_time": 190952.0,
      "text": "I can talk to you over it without worrying"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190952.0,
      "end_time": 193811.0,
      "text": "about what we in fact now know is happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193811.0,
      "end_time": 196261.0,
      "text": "without worrying about the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196261.0,
      "end_time": 198207.0,
      "text": "that not only will surveillance be happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198207.0,
      "end_time": 201245.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;ll be done by people who may abuse the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201245.0,
      "end_time": 202451.0,
      "text": "So in fact, something we realized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 202451.0,
      "end_time": 203859.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t just use the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 203860.0,
      "end_time": 205545.0,
      "text": "we have to worry about"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205545.0,
      "end_time": 209119.0,
      "text": "what the underlying infrastructure of the whole thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 209119.0,
      "end_time": 213315.0,
      "text": "is it in fact of a quality that we need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213315.0,
      "end_time": 218264.0,
      "text": "We revel in the fact that we have this wonderful free speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218264.0,
      "end_time": 221302.0,
      "text": "We can tweet, and oh, lots and lots of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221302.0,
      "end_time": 224227.0,
      "text": "can see our tweets, except when they can&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224227.0,
      "end_time": 227578.0,
      "text": "except when actually Twitter is blocked from their country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227578.0,
      "end_time": 230921.0,
      "text": "or in some way the way we try to express ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 230921.0,
      "end_time": 233856.0,
      "text": "has put some information about the state of ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 233856.0,
      "end_time": 235219.0,
      "text": "the state of the country we live in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 235219.0,
      "end_time": 237703.0,
      "text": "which isn&#39;t available to anybody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 237703.0,
      "end_time": 240684.0,
      "text": "So we must protest and make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240684.0,
      "end_time": 242808.0,
      "text": "that censorship is cut down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 242808.0,
      "end_time": 244382.0,
      "text": "that the web is opened up"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 244382.0,
      "end_time": 246839.0,
      "text": "where there is censorship."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 246839.0,
      "end_time": 249549.0,
      "text": "We love the fact that the web is open."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 249549.0,
      "end_time": 251754.0,
      "text": "It allows us to talk. Anybody can talk to anybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251754.0,
      "end_time": 253591.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t matter who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253592.0,
      "end_time": 254929.0,
      "text": "And then we join these big"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254929.0,
      "end_time": 257582.0,
      "text": "social networking companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 257582.0,
      "end_time": 260944.0,
      "text": "which are in fact effectively built as silos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 260944.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262733.0,
      "text": "so that it&#39;s much easier to talk to somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 262733.0,
      "end_time": 264567.0,
      "text": "in the same social network"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 264567.0,
      "end_time": 266890.0,
      "text": "than it is to talk to somebody in a different one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 266890.0,
      "end_time": 271264.0,
      "text": "so in fact we&#39;re sometimes limiting ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 271264.0,
      "end_time": 274190.0,
      "text": "And we also have, if you&#39;ve read the book about the filter bubble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 274190.0,
      "end_time": 276158.0,
      "text": "the filter bubble phenomenon is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 276158.0,
      "end_time": 277960.0,
      "text": "we love to use machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 277960.0,
      "end_time": 280920.0,
      "text": "which help us find stuff we like."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 280920.0,
      "end_time": 282433.0,
      "text": "So we love it when we&#39;re bathed in"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282434.0,
      "end_time": 284166.0,
      "text": "what things we like to click on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 284166.0,
      "end_time": 286326.0,
      "text": "and so the machine automatically feeds us"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 286326.0,
      "end_time": 287810.0,
      "text": "the stuff that we like and we end up"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 287810.0,
      "end_time": 292710.0,
      "text": "with this rose-colored spectacles view of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292710.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "called a filter bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296203.0,
      "text": "So here are some of the things which maybe"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296203.0,
      "end_time": 299294.0,
      "text": "threaten the social web we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 299295.0,
      "end_time": 301224.0,
      "text": "What sort of web do you want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 301224.0,
      "end_time": 304662.0,
      "text": "I want one which is not fragmented into lots of pieces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 304662.0,
      "end_time": 306844.0,
      "text": "as some countries have been suggesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 306845.0,
      "end_time": 309945.0,
      "text": "they should do in reaction to recent surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309945.0,
      "end_time": 313628.0,
      "text": "I want a web which has got, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 313628.0,
      "end_time": 316587.0,
      "text": "is a really good basis for democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 316588.0,
      "end_time": 321165.0,
      "text": "I want a web where I can use healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 321165.0,
      "end_time": 322920.0,
      "text": "with privacy and where there&#39;s a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 322920.0,
      "end_time": 325900.0,
      "text": "of health data, clinical data is available"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 325900.0,
      "end_time": 327200.0,
      "text": "to scientists to do research."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 327200.0,
      "end_time": 330710.0,
      "text": "I want a web where the other 60 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 330710.0,
      "end_time": 333490.0,
      "text": "get on board as fast as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 333500.0,
      "end_time": 337668.0,
      "text": "I want a web which is such a powerful basis for innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 337668.0,
      "end_time": 339510.0,
      "text": "that when something nasty happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 339510.0,
      "end_time": 341380.0,
      "text": "some disaster strikes, that we can respond"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 341380.0,
      "end_time": 345159.0,
      "text": "by building stuff to respond to it very quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 345160.0,
      "end_time": 348900.0,
      "text": "So this is just some of the things that I want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 348900.0,
      "end_time": 350525.0,
      "text": "from a big list, obviously it&#39;s longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 350526.0,
      "end_time": 351767.0,
      "text": "You have your list."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 351767.0,
      "end_time": 354541.0,
      "text": "I want us to use this 25th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 354541.0,
      "end_time": 357534.0,
      "text": "to think about what sort of a web we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 357534.0,
      "end_time": 359233.0,
      "text": "You can go to webat25.org"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 359233.0,
      "end_time": 360236.0,
      "text": "and find some links."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 360236.0,
      "end_time": 361292.0,
      "text": "There are lots of sites where people"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 361292.0,
      "end_time": 364300.0,
      "text": "have started to put together a Magna Carta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 364400.0,
      "end_time": 365530.0,
      "text": "a bill of rights for the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 365530.0,
      "end_time": 367420.0,
      "text": "How about we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 367430.0,
      "end_time": 371670.0,
      "text": "How about we decide, these are, in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 371670.0,
      "end_time": 375330.0,
      "text": "becoming fundamental rights, the right to communicate with whom I want."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 375330.0,
      "end_time": 377288.0,
      "text": "What would be on your list for that Magna Carta?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 377288.0,
      "end_time": 380156.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s crowdsource a Magna Carta"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 380156.0,
      "end_time": 382398.0,
      "text": "for the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 382398.0,
      "end_time": 384490.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do that this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 384490.0,
      "end_time": 387797.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s use the energy from the 25th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 387797.0,
      "end_time": 390409.0,
      "text": "to crowdsource a Magna Carta"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 390409.0,
      "end_time": 391891.0,
      "text": "to the web. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 391891.0,
      "end_time": 396397.0,
      "text": "Thank you. And do me a favor, will you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 396397.0,
      "end_time": 398962.0,
      "text": "Fight for it for me. Okay? Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 398963.0,
      "end_time": 402950.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}